body_html: @davideb91 That article is somewhat outdated. The model files are now downloaded automatically by Bazel, which is why you're getting conflicts with the manually downloaded ones. You can either delete the files from assets/, or remove the dependencies on the file archives in the tensorflow/examples/android/BUILD file.
